    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2219190/extras/b0bca3150bfe6d6ce3c83248ab930c6e.avif?t=1757668826\" width=616 height=64 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >现在需要控制你的双手去把那些轻微歪斜的物体摆正。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可能偶尔会让你抓狂，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但是不要急，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你大概是能够做到的。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《平衡100》是一款使用双手精准摆放物品的游戏，有点难，但是只要冷静与耐心，即可完成它。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2219190/extras/c558e127f7f6e35bdf5bf6dd45875442.poster.avif?t=1757668826\" width=616 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2219190/extras/c558e127f7f6e35bdf5bf6dd45875442.webm?t=1757668826\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2219190/extras/c558e127f7f6e35bdf5bf6dd45875442.mp4?t=1757668826\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以：</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >调整井盖的旋转角度。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >收拾好混乱的药丸与数据线。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >把美术馆里的画作摆正。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >让星星练成一条线。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >甚至能把比萨斜塔扶正。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >请注意：<strong>《平衡100》</strong>是免费游戏<strong>《平衡97.261/100》</strong>的完整版。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >序章《平衡97.261/100》的游戏内容已占《平衡100》的一半左右，由于本作的操作比较实验性，所以您可以在购买前先进行序章的体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本游戏也支持多人模式，一人控制一个手，希望你与你的伙伴能达到同步率100%。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2219190/extras/b0bca3150bfe6d6ce3c83248ab930c6e.avif?t=1757668826\" width=616 height=64 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >关于开发者</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我是<strong>流贾君liujiajun</strong>，这是我第<strong>六</strong>部上Steam的游戏，希望你能喜欢我的作品，感谢你的游玩。</p>",
